 (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/10974/', '', 'Megestrol acetate, Estetrol, Ulipristal, Estradiol, Megestrol acetate, Progesterone, Estradiol', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Ozanimod, More', 1767369485);
